title: Courtesy Patrol, High Speed Internet, Covered Parking
posting_body: ['Welcome to The Trellis at Lake HighlandsSavor every day at The Trellis at Lake Highlands.', "Just 8 miles from downtown Dallas, we're a first-class gated community offering resort style amenities!", 'Our recently renovated community includes patios, faux wood flooring, granite countertops, wood burning fireplaces, dishwashers and more!', 'Tenants enjoy access to our sparkling pool, tennis court, garden and an outdoor kitchen.', 'Enjoy features such free covered parking, controlled access gates and visitor parking for your guest.', 'Have a pet?', 'The Trellis is pet friendly!', 'We would love to share what makes The Trellis at Lake Highlands the best place to call home.', 'Drop by, give us a call or e-mail today!', 'Professionally Managed by Cirrus Asset Management, Inc., TX - License # 9003183', '-24 Hour Emergency Maintenance Guarantee', '-Courtyard', '-Patio/Balcony', '-2 blocks from Lake Highlands Town Center and Dart Rail Station', '-Controlled Access/Gated', '-Carport', '-Electronic Thermostat', '-Minutes away from White Rock Lake', '-Faux Wood Flooring in all units', '-Popular Townhome Style Floorplans Available', '-On-Site Maintenance', '-View', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
